All good things must come to an end. 

With the start of 2024, it's time for us to bid adieu to our debut original collection - which means - get it while stock lasts.

I am so grateful for each and every person who has collected one of these hand wrought treasures. Elppin OG collection 2018-2024. 

There's no better way to commemorate this moment and show our gratitude than by giving away a set of our cherished Elppin Brooches - our inception piece - the original reason for our existence as an art project & jewelry brand.
